UserStory: As an user I must be able to sign up using name.
As an user I must be able to login using email and password.
As an user I must be able to login to the phptravel site.
As an user I must be able to Navigate to Flights tab.
As an user I must be able to  Enter the source location.
As an user I must be able to  Enter the destination location.
As an user I must be able to Select the departure date
As an user I must be able to  Select number of passengers based on age
As an user I must be able to Select class ( Economy etc )
As an user I must be able to  Select return date if round trip is selected
As an user I must be able to Select flights by clicking on search and check the results.
As a user, I want to select login via FB account
As a user, I must login via google
As a user, I must login with a mobile number
As a user, I must be able to login with an email id
As a user, I must be able to verify mobile number using OTP
As a user, I must enter user name and password
